            . On the evening of the 9th of July last, the two prisoners came into my shop to buy a pair of boots; Vickers tried a pair on, which he said were too big; he said he would fetch his mother; he went towards the place, where the boots were hung before he came in; and I supposed, he hung them up. They both went out of the shop; a woman told me they had taken a pair of boots, and I then missed them.</p>
